Problem Definition for MySql
1. Create a database – ‘registration_trainee’
2. Create a table ‘Department’ with following fields:
a. ID (Primary key)
b. Name 

3. Add one field for the Department in registration form
a. Which will be combo box containing list of departments added in ‘Department’ 


4. Create a Table ‘Employee’ with following fields:
a. ID (Primary key)
b. Every field of registration form.
c. For profile picture, store the location where file has been uploaded.


5. Create a page which will list all employees with following details:
a. Full Name.
b. Name of Department s/he is working.
c. Link to edit their registration details where he should be able to update his details.
d. Listing must be in ascending order of First name.